name: Shree Ganpati
description: Supplying a broad assortment of Food Gra
overview:
Inaugurated in the year 2006, we, “Shree Ganpati Enterprises”, are successfully ranked amongst the top traders, exporters and suppliers of a comprehensive assortment Food Grains, Basmati Rice, Non Basmati Rice, Chickpea, Maize, Soybean Meal, Mustard Meal, etc. Our wide range includes 1121 Parboiled (Sella) Rice, 1121 Steam Rice, White Pusa Basmati Rice, Pusa Steam Basmati Rice, Premium Basmati Rice, Long Grain Parboiled Rice, Matta Rice, Golden Sella Rice, Short Grain Rice, etc.

Our Product Range: 1121 Basmati Rice Non Basmati Rice Chickpea Maize Soybean Meal Mustard Meal

Our Quality Assurance: We have selected an adept team of experienced quality inspectors, who conducts stringent tests on all our procured Food Grains, Basmati Rice, Non Basmati Rice, Chickpea, Maize, Soybean Meal, Mustard Meal, etc.

Customer Satisfaction: Being a client oriented firm, we strive hard to maintain the excellence of our offered products in order to provide utmost satisfaction to the clients. Our offered range is sourced from some of the reliable vendors of the industry in total compliance with the universal quality standards.

Our Vendor Base: Backed by rich vendor base, we have been able to satisfy the bulk requirements of our valuable clients in timely manner. Our wide network of vendors endeavors hard to understand the variegated needs of the clients and further provide the entire product range in accordance with the international standards.
